To run the client program properly, you need to install the JDBC from mysql website. 

(Connector/J)


1. install the latest version as a .zip
2. unzip, and add the folder to the referenced libraries folder under java projects/Inventory2/referenced libraries
3. the connect statement will try to use the database URL to connect.
4. after connecting, SQL queries can be sent. Refer to MYSQL documentation for how to send queries and receive data.

